# ddharmon GUI environment.
# Loaded by systemd (EnvironmentFile=) in production; loaded by load_dotenv() when run manually.
# Copy to the deploy root as `.env` and fill in. Keep this file OUT of git (.env is gitignored).

# --- LLM classify (optional) -----------------------------------------------------------------
# Required ONLY for classifyMode = sync | batch. The default classifyMode "none" runs the full
# cluster + value-subcluster + CDE-anchor pipeline with NO LLM call and NO key needed.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# --- optional overrides (defaults shown as comments) -----------------------------------------
# Directory holding the CDE catalog flat TSVs (cdeSet = endorsed -> nih_endorsed_flat.tsv,
# cdeSet = full -> all_cdes_flat.tsv). The catalog is NOT in git (data/cde/ is
# gitignored) — see deploy/README.md step 5 for how to put it on the server.
# DDHARMON_CDE_DIR=$DEPLOY_DIR/data/cde

# Scratch dir for per-job uploads + Anthropic Batch artifacts (one subdir per jobId).
# DDHARMON_UI_WORK=$DEPLOY_DIR/.ddharmon_ui

# Embedding model cache. Set in the systemd unit so the first-run download lands inside the
# deploy dir (ProtectSystem=strict); override here only if you relocate the cache.
# HF_HOME=$DEPLOY_DIR/.cache/huggingface
# SENTENCE_TRANSFORMERS_HOME=$DEPLOY_DIR/.cache/sentence-transformers
